==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Scaraboid
<hw>Scar"a*boid</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[<ets>Scarab</ets>
+ <ets>-oid</ets>.]</ety> <fld>(Zool.)</fld> <def>Of or pertaining to
the family <fam>Scarabaeidae</fam>, an extensive group which includes
the Egyptian scarab, the tumbledung, and many similar lamellicorn
beetles.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Scaraboid</ent>⟦br⟧

